Just a small town boy…. 

Went back to where it all started ! I had @herro_kristine the city girl come see country livin’

First Stop:
Dropped into Coffey County Airport to join up with my best friend @planeboydan!  Love you ! 
We grabbed a Cherokee 180 & made a trip to Miami County Airport for We B Smokin’ Bbq #IYKYK Met @teriauten w/ Monroe & headed back to beat the rain 🌧️ Annual flight review complete ✅

Second Stop: 
Westphalia, Ks - Born & Raised - Stopped by Westphalia grade school to say hello • Mrs Falls my 2nd grade teacher hasn’t changed a bit. The same sweet person I remember. 

Stopped by my Grandma Annie’s Bar & Grill where I was first influenced with live music & pool and of course nightlife and general life lessons 😀 

Then I met the nice new owner of the home I grew up in , I was able to walk around with him and his kids and tell him stories of the house - he seemed to enjoy it as much as I did. For example the chimney was built by my grandpa and that my mom @rondoo49 actually lived on this property as well. It was a pleasant visit. 

Fulfilling day & I hope to make it back more ❤️ I have some ideas

PS Thank you @dana.hess3 for always being so welcoming & preparing the best dinners 🥩 when I just drop in. Love your family & see you soon. @tegan.hess @carson_hess0 #dannythedad
